## Which license applies to you?

| Use Case | License | Cost |
|----------|---------|------|
| Personal / open-source projects | AGPL v3 | Free |
| Academic / research | AGPL v3 | Free |
| Internal company use (source stays open) | AGPL v3 | Free |
| Closed-source product integration | Commercial | Paid |
| Hosted / managed service (SaaS) | Commercial | Paid |
| Redistribution without source disclosure | Commercial | Paid |

