## Summary

- If you use, modify, or distribute SwarmAI and make your changes available
  under AGPL v3, you can use it for free.
- If you want to use SwarmAI in a closed-source product, embed it in a
  proprietary service, or avoid AGPL obligations, you need a commercial license.
